00540         template <typename T, precision P>
00541         GLM_FUNC_QUALIFIER tmat2x2<T, P> operator*
00542         (
00543                 tmat4x2<T, P> const & m1,
00544                 tmat2x4<T, P> const & m2
00545         )
00546         {
00547                 T const SrcA00 = m1[0][0];
00548                 T const SrcA01 = m1[0][1];
00549                 T const SrcA10 = m1[1][0];
00550                 T const SrcA11 = m1[1][1];
00551                 T const SrcA20 = m1[2][0];
00552                 T const SrcA21 = m1[2][1];
00553                 T const SrcA30 = m1[3][0];
00554                 T const SrcA31 = m1[3][1];
00555 
00556                 T const SrcB00 = m2[0][0];
00557                 T const SrcB01 = m2[0][1];
00558                 T const SrcB02 = m2[0][2];
00559                 T const SrcB03 = m2[0][3];
00560                 T const SrcB10 = m2[1][0];
00561                 T const SrcB11 = m2[1][1];
00562                 T const SrcB12 = m2[1][2];
00563                 T const SrcB13 = m2[1][3];
00564 
00565                 tmat2x2<T, P> Result(tmat2x2<T, P>::_null);
00566                 Result[0][0] = SrcA00 * SrcB00 + SrcA10 * SrcB01 + SrcA20 * SrcB02 + SrcA30 * SrcB03;
00567                 Result[0][1] = SrcA01 * SrcB00 + SrcA11 * SrcB01 + SrcA21 * SrcB02 + SrcA31 * SrcB03;
00568                 Result[1][0] = SrcA00 * SrcB10 + SrcA10 * SrcB11 + SrcA20 * SrcB12 + SrcA30 * SrcB13;
00569                 Result[1][1] = SrcA01 * SrcB10 + SrcA11 * SrcB11 + SrcA21 * SrcB12 + SrcA31 * SrcB13;
00570                 return Result;
00571         }
